From 81594b8d9ea329fa5405612b8a78167dce7b899b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Damien Caliste <dcaliste@free.fr>
Date: Wed, 4 Mar 2026 22:38:34 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 1/9] [mkcal] Adopt the deprecated notebook API.

Since KF6, this API is removed from KCalendarCore.
For a transition period, let's adopt the API here.
This should allow to continue to use ExtendedCalendar
for a while.
---
 src/extendedcalendar.cpp | 196 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/extendedcalendar.h   | 134 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/extendedstorage.cpp  |  12 ++-
 src/extendedstorage.h    |   8 +-
 tests/tst_storage.cpp    |   2 +-
 5 files changed, 347 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

